Setup
------
- C++
- OpenCV4
- understanding makefile
- onnxruntime package (for depth anything v2)


Tasks
-----
1. Read an image from a file and display it.
filename - imgDisplay.cpp

2. Display live video
filename - vidDisplay.cpp
needs webcam for live video capture
save image to s file if user presses 's'

3. Display grey  scale live video
update vidDisplay.cpp
use 'g' key to turn on and off the grey scale filter


4. Display alternative greyscale live video. 

5. Sepia tone filter

6. 5x5 blur filter

7. Sobel filter as separable filters

8. Gradient magnitude image from sobel filter. 

9. Filter that Blurs and quanitzes a color image.

10. Detect faces in an image

11. Use depth anything v2 to get depth estimates

12. Custom effects


